      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 54 初九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 54 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九：歸妹以娣，跛能履，征吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first NINE, undivided, shows the younger sister married off in a position ancillary to the real wife. (It suggests the idea of) a person lame on one leg who yet manages to tramp along. Going forward will be fortunate.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
