      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 54 九二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 54 九二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二：眇能視，利幽人之貞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second NINE, undivided, shows her blind of one eye, and yet able to see. There will be advantage in her maintaining the firm correctness of a solitary widow.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
