      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 54 六三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六三：歸妹以須，反歸以娣。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third SIX, divided, shows the younger sister who was to be married off in a mean position. She returns and accepts an ancillary position.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
