      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 54 九四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九四：歸妹愆期，遲歸有時。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth NINE, undivided, shows the younger sister who is to be married off protracting the time. She may be late in being married, but the time will come.</seg>
      </tuv>
